Package TestCase_Automation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BrowserWebDriver  
    DataProviders
    This class houses the test data that drives this "Data Driven" Test Suite.
    Image
    Images tests class handles all image tag related tests.
    Link
    Link class - handles all anchor element related tests and methods.
    Locators  
    Logging
    Test result Logging / Reporting class using log4j Log file name and path are defined as a system property so log4j2.xml file can access.
    Page
    Page element test class - common methods shared among page elements
    TestCase
    This is the base test case class - This class reads test data from excel utilizing methods defined in DataProviders class.
    Users
    Users class handles all login, registration related tests
    Vars
    This class defines Test Case static variable and constants
